Hello all,

I just released the first version of my C++ library for accessing the
contents of ARC files:

              http://www.sourceforge.net/projects/libarc

It is known to build and work on Mac OS X (10.3) and RedHat Linux
7.3. I will test on other Unixen as time allows.

The library is released under the BSD license.

Share and enjoy.
